# Terraform
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
voc.plan
crash.log
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Build artifacts
terraform/.build/
scripts/bin/

# Secrets / keys (never commit)
*.pem
*.tfvars.local
*.auto.tfvars
secrets.auto.tfvars

# pack_devel: contains a live Palette API token; pack-central is a large reference clone
pack_devel/instructions.txt
pack_devel/pack-central/
pack_devel/**/charts/*.tgz

# pack_devel/cmargo: CM/Palette SDK example — strip live creds before any commit.
# notes + that CLAUDE.md carry a literal Palette token; acr-secret.yaml's
# .dockerconfigjson decodes to the ACR registry password; the cmd/*/main.go files
# hardcode the same Palette token (+ an edgeHostToken in deploy-cluster).
pack_devel/cmargo/notes
pack_devel/cmargo/CLAUDE.md
pack_devel/cmargo/cluster-profile/argocd/acr-secret.yaml
pack_devel/cmargo/cluster-profile/cmd/**/main.go
